      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {},
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "The seven-package split is a map of runtime and ownership boundaries, not seven pieces that every user assembles by hand. Some seams isolate genuinely incompatible environments; three others are current judgment calls and may collapse."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
